        "Description": [
            "I need you to pick up a package and get rid of it. [Timed]\n\nDon't give a crap where you take it as long as it's off-world and no one ever finds it. [Stops]",
            "I don't know what happened, and I don't really care, but someone made a pretty big mess and we're looking for a discrete individual to make the problem vanish by disposing of a package. \n\nPretty simple, really. It's not like I'm asking you to [FakeOut]. [Stops][Timed]",
            "Just got an urgent comm from some people I used to run with. They're not saying much but it sounds like they had a pretty serious 'accident.' Want someone to take care of dumping a package off-world. \n\n[Stops]I'd plan on getting your ship's cargo bay washed when this is done. [Timed]",
            "Got a request for a cleaner. There's a package wrapped up and ready to drag off-world, just need a ship to take it somewhere that security won't think to look. \n\n[Stops]And don't even think about opening it up. Whatever's in there is better left sealed up.\u00a0[Timed]",
            "Best part of our line of work? You never know what you're going to be doing one day to the next. \n\nTake today for instance. Today you're going to be making a package disappear off-world. [Stops][Timed]\n\nHow 'bout that? Who knows what you'll be doing tomorrow, right?",
            "I need you to [FakeOut] ... Ha! Wouldn't that be awesome? \n\nKidding aside, I need you to grab a package and dump it off-world. [Timed] [Stops]Thanks."
        ],
